{
  "texts": [
    "AI systems rely on extensive data, making institutions vulnerable to breaches and misuse of personal information [45,46].",
    "Institutions must adopt governance measures to protect student privacy and balance technological innovation with ethical standards [47].",
    "This study examines how activity-based learning and ChatGPT affect students' academic achievement.",
    "It compares ChatGPT to traditional approaches and assesses its pros and cons as a teaching tool.",
    "Activity-based learning improves students' engagement, motivation, and critical thinking, while ChatGPT provides interactive learning and individualized support to help them comprehend and explore complicated concepts [29]."
  ]
}